window.bookSummaryJSON = "First, the mystery man in the church with a bullet-wound. Then, the riddle of a dead man's buried treasure...the curious conduct of a caretaker after a fatal riding accident...the corpse and a tape-measure...the girl framed for theft...and the suspect accused of stabbing his wife with a dagger. <p>Here are six gripping cases with one thing in common: the astonishing deductive powers of Miss Marple.</p>"; 
